extends BusRefImpl<BaseAcscBus<?,?>>
implements AcscBusFault
    An implementation of the model object 'Bus Fault'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Fault Type
    • Fault Code
    • ZLG Fault
    • ZLL Fault
    • Fault Result
